data.description: This BEAUTIFUL 4 bedroom 2.5 bath brick home sits on a quarter of an acre lot in a wonderful neighborhood! This house has a split floor plan with a large master bedroom and bathroom which includes a whirlpool tub and walk in shower. The kitchen has stunning white cabinets and granite counter tops with bar seating. Additional bonus' to this home are the stainless steel appliances, granite countertops in bathroom/kitchen/laundry room, tile flooring, 3 car garage, large entry way. Laundry room also has a sink for all your clean up needs! This home could also be used as an INVESTMENT PROPERTY. It is currently leased. *CONTACT LISTING AGENT FOR LEASE DETAILS* Sq footage needs official measurements.
